Name: Stage 6
Desc: Learn about the Beacon block. It doubles the value of adjacent blocks after merging.

Name: Stage 8
Desc: Learn about the Hub block. When any adjacent block's value doubles, this block's value doubles as well.

Name: Stage 11
Desc: Learn about the Power Core block. Adds n Enhanced Moves upon the next level up after merging n times.

Name: Stage 12
Desc: Learn about the Ballast block. It's immovable but mergeable and becomes a Power Core block after merging.
